(firstQuint)Probiotics Effect on Glucose and Lipid Metabolism and Gut Microbiota in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes.

 This study aims to evaluate the effect of probiotics on the improvement of glucose and lipid metabolism, as well as the gut microbiota.

Baseline, 1 month and 3 month data will be collected and put into analysis to provide some suggestions on the probiotics use in the clinical practice for type 2 diabetes patients.

